<p>This protocol combines GH elevation with targeted tissue repair for maximum training recovery. Run for 8&ndash;12 weeks before taking a 4-week break.</p>

<table class="tbl">
<thead><tr><th>Timing</th><th>Compound</th><th>Dose</th><th>Notes</th></tr></thead>
<tbody>
<tr><td><strong>Mon&ndash;Fri AM</strong></td><td>TB-500</td><td>500 mcg</td><td class="g">Subcutaneous injection</td></tr>
<tr><td><strong>Mon&ndash;Fri Post-Workout</strong></td><td>BPC-157</td><td>250 mcg</td><td class="g">Inject near target muscle group</td></tr>
<tr><td><strong>Mon&ndash;Fri Pre-Bed</strong></td><td>CJC-1295 + Ipamorelin</td><td>100 mcg each</td><td class="g">Fasted, empty stomach</td></tr>
<tr><td><strong>Sat&ndash;Sun</strong></td><td>Off</td><td>n/a</td><td class="y">Recovery days</td></tr>
